Package: nivo.bubblechart
Title: Interactive Bubble Charts for 'Shiny' Using 'Nivo'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Anastasiia", "Kostiv", , "akostiv11@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates interactive bubble chart visualizations for 'Shiny' applications
    using the 'Nivo' circle packing library. Provides an 'htmlwidgets' wrapper around
    the 'Nivo' circle packing chart, enabling hierarchical data visualization with
    customizable colors, labels, and interactive features including click and hover events.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DataRacerEdu/nivo.bubblechart
